                  </ui>
                  <value>
                     <text xliff:rid="A752D1BA-A026-4808-B6D8-A187C179A8C8"> We, Delval Flow Controls Pvt. Ltd. hereby warranty the satisfactory performance of our products being supplied to you against above mentioned purchase order no. and invoice no.	   Warranty for the supplied product will be limited for a period of 36 months from the date of supply.For the bought out components, the respective manufacturers warranty applies.However we will provide all necessary assistance to the buyer.   In case of any product found faulty due to faulty materials, processes or assembly, M/s Delval Flow Controls Pvt. Ltd. will repair or replace it as its own discretion, free of cost within the said warranty period. In such case our liability will be limited only to the purchased product and we will not be any way liable for any direct or indirect costs, expenses, damages to the properties, misuse of product and any monetary loss or production loss incurred by the purchaser.   This warranty will not be applicable   1. If the instructions or precautions mentioned in the IOM are not followed properly. 2. In Case there is any improper handling or misuse of product.   For, Delval Flow Controls Pvt. Ltd.       Authorized by   QA Dept.</text>
                  </value>
                  <font baselineShift="0pt" typeface="Times New Roman"/>
                  <margin bottomInset="0.5mm" leftInset="0.5mm" rightInset="0.5mm" topInset="0.5mm"/>
